":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"其實有時真係唔係唔想傾，男人唔想講錯嘢就寧願自己收埋下，你想面對面傾，可能佢驚自己一講錯就變嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ba0791e3a5ce8f8eed1187f3c608a661bef348","tid":2455684,"uid":394713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16e200614b03426a6fdd7247a636242fd276761","tid":2455684,"uid":395295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"你平時係咪chur 得佢好勁"},{"pid":"2239dc449df60845f3ca95a267fbbe1ed9c22a10","tid":2455684,"uid":204024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"前幾日經歷都同樓主一樣<br />\n一直以嚟我都太過chur 因為咁已經嗌過好多次交<br />\n前幾日個次佢終於頂唔順 話要靜下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都反省左自己 知道自己衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實本身都打定輸數 覺得靜得就實分硬啦<br />\n但好好彩嘅係佢隔左一兩日就搵返我 依家冇事啦<br />\n我覺得如果仲有愛嘅話 其實對方唔會唔捨得放棄你嘅<br />\n但大前題係你要show到比對方睇你有反省到 唔係嘅話就算比你一齊返 下次都係因為同一個問題再嘈過<br />\n好快就會幾愛都會攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議樓主依幾日都自己沉澱下先 <br />\n諗清楚大家嘅相處模式邊到出左問題 唔好急住搵對方<br />\n你越搵佢佢越覺得大壓力<br />\n依段期間係會好辛苦 係咁懷疑自己 等俾人判死刑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你除左調整自己心態之外其實都冇野做到 所以唔好諗咁多自己控制唔到嘅野啦 <br />\n加油樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利：好返但係都係覺得冇一開始咁sweet <br />\n我明大家都要啲時間 唯有調節好自己心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534c2e4f49bf9089f0b7beefd7254a27a30698c1","tid":2455684,"uid":61180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">哈</span> 又多一對分手 爽！"},{"pid":"5e4c881e25fd9f64e85819c54305e9ab3a646d6d","tid":2455684,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"又唔自己諗下點解人地會覺得同你傾就等同嘈交<br />\n肯定係平時惡撚到閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a636a99d0962bec06f3854fc6401474fce7689c","tid":2455684,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"醫左個肚仔先啦"},{"pid":"82ad362e26aecfbc637300071ed264964e8fe4f0","tid":2455684,"uid":395295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46ba0791e3a5ce8f8eed1187f3c608a661bef348","tid":2455684,"uid":394713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16e200614b03426a6fdd7247a636242fd276761","tid":2455684,"uid":395295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"你平時係咪chur 得佢好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"no... 平時都一星期見一兩次淨係"},{"pid":"e4deeedbe01213c005c1962ca962267dc9617986","tid":2455684,"uid":395295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e4c881e25fd9f64e85819c54305e9ab3a646d6d","tid":2455684,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"又唔自己諗下點解人地會覺得同你傾就等同嘈交<br />\n肯定係平時惡撚到閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:08:02.000Z","msg":"平時佢一飲完酒就會鬧我..."}]}